{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Prompter\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Prompter for working with subtitles (regions/items) in REAPER\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Shows regions or text items as a scrollable list\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Automatically highlights current line based on playback position\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Quick navigation by clicking on a line (+ copies text to clipboard)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Customizable fonts, colors and sizes for regions and items separately\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Search with highlighted results\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab "All elements" mode - combines regions and items in one timeline-sorted list\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Smooth scrolling and current line magnification\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Autostart SubOverlay when Prompter starts (optional)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Requirements\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab ReaImGui (install via ReaPack)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab JS_ReaScript Extensions (install via ReaPack)\sa180\par}
}

