{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Convert SWS subtitles to regions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Convert SWS S&M subtitles to full timeline regions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Reads currently open (saved) project .rpp file\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Extracts <S&M_SUBTITLE blocks from  and maps them to marker indices\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Uses marker timing pairs (MARKER lines) to create regions with full subtitle text\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Deletes all existing timeline regions and recreates them with full texts\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Usage\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Save your project in REAPER, run this script from Actions \u8594 ? ReaScript\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Script will abort if the project is not saved\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Note:} Backup project before running!\par}
}

