{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Import text items from subtitles} - Import SRT/ASS subtitles as text items\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Import regions from subtitles} - Import SRT/ASS subtitles as project regions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Export items to SRT} - Export text items from selected track to SRT file\par}
