{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Create text items from regions} - Convert project regions to text items on new track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Create regions from text items} - Convert text items on selected track to project regions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Convert SWS subtitles to regions} - Convert SWS S&M subtitles to full timeline regions\sa180\par}
